lead_paragraph: Mo Farah returned to the scene of his 2012 Olympic glory and completed his preparations for the defense of his distance double in Rio with a crushing sub-13-minute victory in the 5,000 meters at the London Diamond League meeting on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Athletics: Dominant Farah Warms Up for Rio in Style
